MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 1074

CREATING AND DESIGNATING A BUILDING, TO BE KNOWN AS EAST CYBER GATE BUILDING, WHICH STANDS ON A PARCEL OF LAND LOCATED AT 169 EDSA, MANDALUYONG CITY, AS AN INFORMATION TECHNOLOGY BUILDING PURSUANT TO REPUBLIC ACT NO. 7916, AS AMENDED BY REPUBLIC ACT NO. 8748

Pursuant to the powers vested in me under Republic Act No. 7916, otherwise known as the Special Economic Zone Act of 1995, as amended by Republic Act No. 8748, and upon recommendation of the Board of Directors of the Philippine Economic Zone Authority, I, GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO , President of the Republic of the Philippines, by virtue of the powers vested in me by law, do hereby create and designate as Information Technology Building , subject to the provisions of Republic Act No. 7916 as amended, its Implementing Rules and Regulations, Resolution Nos. 00-411 and 04-033, dated December 29, 2000 and February 17, 2004, respectively, of the Board of Directors of the Philippine Economic Zone Authority, the EAST CYBER GATE BUILDING , containing an area of NINE HUNDRED NINETY (990) SQUARE METERS, more or less, located at 169 EDSA, Mandaluyong City, as defined by the following technical description:

